glbic_b1->+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+ 0x0804b168
          LOW MEM

Note that buffer2 points to 0x0804b168, but as far as glibc is concerned,
buffer2 starts at 0x804b178 (minus 8 bytes) as allocated heap segments
can have prev_size and size fields set. 

